  <description type="morphology">Plants tight, compact mats, 1–3(–5) dm wide. Aerial flowering stems mostly erect, 0.1–2 dm. Leaf blades usually elliptic, 1–5 × 0.3–1.5 cm, densely tomentose abaxially, tomentose to floccose and greenish adaxially. Inflorescences umbellate; branches 4–20 cm. Involucres turbinate to campanulate, 3–8 mm. Flowers 3–7 mm, including 0.3–1 mm stipelike base; perianth bright yellow. 2n = 80.</description>
